milestones.description: Mohammad Nabi has become the top wicket-taker for AFG in ODIs with 90 wickets, going past Dawlat Zadran's 88
Porterfield has scored 23 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, the most for IRE breaking Paul Stirling's record

stories.title: Stirling, Dockrell spearhead 2-1 series win for Ireland
stories.subTitle: Afghanistan v Ireland, 3rd ODI, Sharjah
stories.seoTitle: Paul Stirling, George Dockrell spearhead 2-1 series win for Ireland
stories.summary: George Dockrell's first four-for in nearly three years was followed by a century from Paul Stirling, who struck 101 off 97 balls, to chase down 178 with 12 overs to spare
stories.byline: The Report by Peter Della Penna in Sharjah
